pod_cpu_usage`.\n  - **Evidence**: `pod_cpu_usage` and `pod_processes` change ratio of 2.0 and 0.6667.\n\n### Detected Metric Keys\n```json\n[\"node_memory_usage_rate\", \"pod_cpu_usage\", \"error_ratio\", \"rrt_max\"]\n```\n\n### Output JSON\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"node_memory_usage_rate\", \"pod_cpu_usage\", \"error_ratio\", \"rrt_max\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-03\",\n      \"reason\": \"node_memory_usage_rate fluctuation causing resource constraints on pods, impacting performance.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Memory usage decreased from 38.93% to 33.83%.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Increased pod_cpu_usage resulting in handling delays.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage spiked with change ratio of 2.0.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n此报告总结了在故障期间检测到的异常，并分析可能的根因与影响。我们将在随后阶段继续详细分析，以确认或否定这些假设。", "trace_analysis_findings": "The trace data has been successfully collected for UUID `6ef260df-97`. Below is the structure of the latency and anomaly metrics observed during the given period.\n\n### Key Findings:\n\n#### Analyzed Traces (Summary):\n| Node Name        | Service Name                | Parent Pod                  | Child Pod                   | Operation                          | Normal Avg. Duration (ms) | Anomaly Avg. Duration (ms) | Anomaly Count |\n|------------------|-----------------------------|-----------------------------|-----------------------------|-------------------------------------|---------------------------|----------------------------|---------------|\n| aiops-k8s-07     | redis                       | cartservice-0               | cartservice-0               | HGET                               | 1739.74                   | 7063.17                    | 1             |\n| aiops-k8s-03     | cartservice                 | checkoutservice-2           | cartservice-2               | POST /hipstershop.CartService/EmptyCa