ckend shows signature high latency linked to `CartService`.\n\nNext steps involve analyzing propagated effects across dependency scopes further against the topology.\n\n### Output JSON:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"latency_spike\", \n    \"cartservice->redis\",\n    \"checkoutservice->cartservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->emailservice\",\n    \"frontend->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"frontend->CurrencyService\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"latency_spike via cartservice->redis\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Redis operation 'HGET' has anomaly multiplier ~4.06x (1739.74ms -> 7063.17ms)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"latency_spike via checkoutservice->cartservice\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CartService operation 'EmptyCart' experiencing anomaly multiplier ~19.71x (2258.79ms -> 44506.5ms)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"emailservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"latency_spike via checkoutservice->emailservice\",\n      \"evidence\": \"EmailService anomalies 'SendOrderConfirmation' ~2.88x (703.33ms -> 2029.67ms)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"slow_operation in frontend->productcatalogservice\",\n      \"evidence\": \"ProductCatalogService experiencing increase (73.75ms -> 184.25ms)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CurrencyService\",\n      \"reason\": \"gradual spikes frontend->currency connection both paths\",\n    }\n    <!-- ... User Decision Pending Rest correlate Extend/Base Service-choice nature evaluator -->\n  \n```\nThe anomaly spans indicate latency propagation links significantly across core entry-edge. Detailed verifies point tending relay analysis module"}
